@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Let Customers Find U Easily!";
}

<h2>@ViewBag.Title</h2>

<div class="page-header" id="Contact">
    <h4>Advertise With US <br /><small>TrendAfrik is a subsidiary of QuickySales Ltd</small></h4>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
        <p><b>How To Join</b></p>

        1. <div class="thumbnail">
            Send your company name, phone number, email to
            info@trendafrik.com or whatsapp to +2348120042929

        </div>
        2.<div class="thumbnail">
            Also Send the picture(s) of materials (traditional textiles, 
            beads making, bags from local textiles, shoes, make up art, 
            fashion designers, etc.) item name, price, description, 
            picture(1 to 4 pics per material) each to the details given above.
        </div>
        3. <div class="thumbnail">
            DONE!.... U don't have to even meet Us! FREE first Month!
            With No obligation to still advertise after the First Month.
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
        <p><b>Frequently Asked Questions</b></p>

        1. <div class="thumbnail">
               <b>What  is Trend Afrik?</b><br />

               Trend Afrik is an online market place. We exist to bring merchants
             (sellers) and buyers of Afrocentric clothing and related goods & services
                together.


        </div>
        2.<div class="thumbnail">
              <b>How does it work?</b><br />

              Merchants send us up to four different pictures and price of each
              product they wish to display on the platform, which we then upload for them. 
              Interested buyers contact the sellers directly and both parties agree on purchase and delivery terms.
        </div>
        3. <div class="thumbnail">
               <b>Does Trend Afrik sell items displayed on behalf of the merchants?</b><br />

               No, Trend Afrik does not sell on behalf of the merchants. The merchants are solely responsible for
               making any sales when contacted by interested buyers. Trend Afrik is only providing a platform for merchants and buyers to meet.
        </div>

        4. <div class="thumbnail">
            <b>Does Trend Afrik make deliveries on behalf of the merchants?</b><br />

               No, Trend Afrik does not make deliveries of items displayed on the site.
               The merchants are solely responsible for delivering items requested by interested buyers. 
               Trend Afrik is only providing a platform for merchants and buyers to meet.
          </div>

        5. <div class="thumbnail">
            <b>Who can sell on Trend Afrik?</b><br />

               Anyone who is a manufacturer, producer, and/or seller of African-themed items.
           <br />
               Clothing accessories like shoes, make up, scarves, beads, hair extensions, etc. do not have to be African themed.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-2" id="hButton1">
    <a class="btn btn-warning" @Html.ActionLink("Back", "Index", "Home")</a>
</div>




